<article id="post-960" class="post-960 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-renovations tag-basement">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/04/renovations-update/" rel="bookmark">Renovations Update</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Since we went off world-hopping, a lot has happened. That&#8217;s not to say the basement is done yet. Sadly, we had hoped for completion by May. A couple of starting delays, and then a labour disruption with our contractor led to a bit of a slowdown. It&#8217;s almost the end of April, which means it&#8217;ll be an Act of God to get the basement done by May.<br />
I think we&#8217;re okay with that. But it can&#8217;t go on much longer. Time&#8217;s a-runnin&#8217; out.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/04/renovations-update/#more-960" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Renovations Update&#8221;</span></a></p>
